OL,5, Potentially abusive men are using a UK 
OL,6, scheme to host Ukrainian refugees - to 
OL,7, contact vulnerable women, BBC News has 
OL,8, learned.                               
OL,10,FThe men, some with a reported history  
OL,11,Fof violence, message the women on      
OL,12,FFacebook groups specially set up to    
OL,13,Fconnect sponsors and hosts.            
OL,15,FSome refugees have also become homeless
OL,16,Fafter relations with hosts broke down  
OL,17,For because housing was not well vetted.
OL,19,FBut a UK government official said      
OL,20,Fsafeguards were in place.              
